{"id": "1205425445659746385", "channel_id": "1202785630715781212", "type": 0, "author_id": "392840163732226058", "author_name": "vegoutdino", "author_bot": false, "content": "這周造物算力+2再加上黑燭+2，\n起手9算力不怕被覺醒卡手，\n也讓水母每次洗牌都能把牌打乾，\n拉蒙娜道中拉報償，菁英BOSS戰拉水母洗牌，\n賣卡先賣攻勢推演，女王劍要拿來棄排充銀鑰，\n水母只是缺個好的力量輔助，\n奧吉爾疊的還是有點慢，但能自帶個易傷是真的好用。", "timestamp": "2024-02-09T08:10:21.967000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-02-09T08:16:12.844000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1205425445424730122", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 14697, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1202785630715781212/1205425445424730122/image.png?ex=69cc2a2d&is=69cad8ad&hm=5b20f833a1747dbc26305db988e284ca12b8c3e840ca2b539ecb22765ac72c37&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1202785630715781212", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "2.1版本后的深海思路与探索", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1211882178007408651", "1174179716706619494"]}
